{"id":914,"parent_id":909,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":914,"title":"Amos 5","subtitle":"","short_title":"Amos","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/5","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 5"],[".studySummary",["i","The people of Israel are exhorted to seek the Lord and do good so that they may live—Their sacrifices to false gods are abhorrent."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/5.1","order":"02.31.005.61280"},["b","1"],"Hear ye this word which I take up against you,",["i","even"],"a lamentation, O house of Israel."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/5.2","order":"02.31.005.61281"},["b","2"],"The virgin of Israel is fallen; she shall no more rise: she is forsaken upon her land;",["i","there is"],"none to raise her up."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/5.3","order":"02.31.005.61282"},["b","3"],"For thus saith the Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],"; The city that went out",["i","by"],"a thousand shall leave an hundred, and that which went forth",["i","by"],"an hundred shall leave ten, to the house of Israel."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/5.4","order":"02.31.005.61283"},["b","4"],"¶For thus saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"unto the house of Israel,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"Seek"],"ye me, and ye shall live:"],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/5.5","order":"02.31.005.61284"},["b","5"],"But seek not Beth-el, nor enter into Gilgal, and pass not to Beer-sheba: for Gilgal shall surely go into captivity, and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"Beth-el"],"shall come to nought."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/5.6","order":"02.31.005.61285"},["b","6"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"Seek"],"the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", and ye shall live; lest he break out like fire in the house of Joseph, and devour",["i","it,"],"and",["i","there be"],"none to quench",["i","it"],"in Beth-el."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/5.7","order":"02.31.005.61286"},["b","7"],"Ye who turn judgment to wormwood, and leave off righteousness in the earth,"],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/5.8","order":"02.31.005.61287"},["b","8"],["i","Seek him"],"that maketh",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"the"],"seven",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"stars"],"and Orion, and turneth the shadow of death into the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_8c"},"morning"],", and maketh the day",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_8d"},"dark"],"with night: that calleth for the",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_8e"},"waters"],"of the sea, and poureth them out upon the face of the earth:",["sup","f"],["a",{"href":"fn_8f"},"The",["span.smallCaps","Lord"]],["i","is"],"his name:"],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/5.9","order":"02.31.005.61288"},["b","9"],"That strengtheneth the spoiled against the strong, so that the spoiled shall come against the fortress."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/5.10","order":"02.31.005.61289"},["b","10"],"They hate him that rebuketh in the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"gate"],", and they abhor him that speaketh uprightly."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/5.11","order":"02.31.005.61290"},["b","11"],"Forasmuch therefore as your treading",["i","is"],"upon the poor, and ye take from him burdens of wheat: ye have",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"built"],"houses of hewn stone, but ye shall not",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"dwell"],"in them; ye have planted pleasant vineyards, but ye shall not drink wine of them."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/5.12","order":"02.31.005.61291"},["b","12"],"For I know your manifold transgressions and your mighty sins: they afflict the just, they take a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"bribe"],", and they",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_12b"},"turn"],"aside the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_12c"},"poor"],"in the gate",["i","from their right."]],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/5.13","order":"02.31.005.61292"},["b","13"],"Therefore the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"prudent"],"shall keep",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"silence"],"in that time; for it",["i","is"],"an evil time."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/5.14","order":"02.31.005.61293"},["b","14"],"Seek",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"good"],", and not",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"evil"],", that ye may live: and so the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", the God of hosts, shall be with you, as ye have spoken."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/5.15","order":"02.31.005.61294"},["b","15"],"Hate the evil, and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"love"],"the good, and establish judgment in the gate: it may be that the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"God of hosts will be gracious unto the remnant of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_15b"},"Joseph"],"."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/5.16","order":"02.31.005.61295"},["b","16"],"Therefore the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", the God of hosts, the Lord, saith thus; Wailing",["i","shall be"],"in all streets; and they shall say in all the highways, Alas! alas! and they shall call the husbandman to mourning, and such as are skilful of lamentation to wailing."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/5.17","order":"02.31.005.61296"},["b","17"],"And in all vineyards",["i","shall be"],"wailing: for I will pass through thee, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/5.18","order":"02.31.005.61297"},["b","18"],"Woe unto you that",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"desire"],"the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_18b"},"day"],"of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"! to what end",["i","is"],"it for you? the day of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],["i","is"],["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_18c"},"darkness"],", and not light."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/5.19","order":"02.31.005.61298"},["b","19"],"As if a man did flee from a lion, and a bear met him; or went into the house, and leaned his hand on the wall, and a serpent bit him."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/5.20","order":"02.31.005.61299"},["b","20"],["i","Shall"],"not the day of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],["i","be"],"darkness, and not light? even very dark, and no brightness in it?"],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/5.21","order":"02.31.005.61300"},["b","21"],"¶I hate, I despise your",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"feast"],"days, and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_21b"},"I"],"will not smell in your",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_21c"},"solemn assemblies"],"."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/5.22","order":"02.31.005.61301"},["b","22"],"Though ye",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"offer"],"me burnt offerings and your meat offerings, I will not",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_22b"},"accept"],["i","them:"],"neither will I regard the peace",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_22c"},"offerings"],"of your fat beasts."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/5.23","order":"02.31.005.61302"},["b","23"],"Take thou away from me the noise of thy songs; for I will not hear the melody of thy viols."],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/5.24","order":"02.31.005.61303"},["b","24"],"But let",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_24a"},"judgment"],"run down as waters, and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_24b"},"righteousness"],"as a mighty stream."],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/5.25","order":"02.31.005.61304"},["b","25"],"Have ye offered unto me sacrifices and offerings in the wilderness forty years, O house of Israel?"],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/5.26","order":"02.31.005.61305"},["b","26"],"But ye have borne the tabernacle of your",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_26a"},"Moloch"],"and Chiun your images, the star of your god, which ye made to yourselves."],["div",{"id":"27","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/5.27","order":"02.31.005.61306"},["b","27"],"Therefore will I cause you to go into captivity beyond Damascus, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", whose name",["i","is"],"The God of hosts."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/5.4a","order":"02.31.005.61307"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/1.20"},"2 Ne. 1:20"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/26.30"},"Mosiah 26:30"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/5.5a","order":"02.31.005.61309"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/amos/3.14"},"Amos 3:14"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/5.6a","order":"02.31.005.61311"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/16.11"},"1 Chr. 16:11"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/37.47"},"Alma 37:47"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/ether/12.41"},"Ether 12:41"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/45.46"},"D&C 45:46"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/88.63"},"88:63"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/101.38"},"101:38"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/5.8a","order":"02.31.005.61313"},["b","8a"],["span.small","IE"],"the Pleiades."],["div",{"id":"8b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/5.8b","order":"02.31.005.61315"},["b","8b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/astronomy"},"TG Astronomy"],"."],["div",{"id":"8c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/5.8c","order":"02.31.005.61317"},["b","8c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/amos/4.13"},"Amos 4:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"8d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/5.8d","order":"02.31.005.61319"},["b","8d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/amos/8.9"},"Amos 8:9"],"."],["div",{"id":"8e","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/5.8e","order":"02.31.005.61321"},["b","8e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/amos/9.6"},"Amos 9:6"],"."],["div",{"id":"8f","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/5.8f","order":"02.31.005.61323"},["b","8f"],["span.small","HEB"],"Jehovah."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/5.10a","order":"02.31.005.61325"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/27.32"},"2 Ne. 27:32"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/5.11a","order":"02.31.005.61327"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/1.13"},"Zeph. 1:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"11b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/5.11b","order":"02.31.005.61329"},["b","11b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/28.30"},"Deut. 28:30"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/5.12a","order":"02.31.005.61331"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/bribe"},"TG Bribe"],"."],["div",{"id":"12b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/5.12b","order":"02.31.005.61333"},["b","12b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/29.21"},"Isa. 29:21"],"."],["div",{"id":"12c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/5.12c","order":"02.31.005.61335"},["b","12c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22.7.7-13"},"Ezek. 22:7 (7–13)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/6.39.37-40"},"Hel. 6:39 (37–40)"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/5.13a","order":"02.31.005.61337"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/prudence"},"TG Prudence"],"."],["div",{"id":"13b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/5.13b","order":"02.31.005.61339"},["b","13b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/prov/17.28.27-28"},"Prov. 17:28 (27–28)"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/5.14a","order":"02.31.005.61341"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/ether/4.12.11-12"},"Ether 4:12 (11–12)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/moro/7.16"},"Moro. 7:16"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/6.13"},"D&C 6:13"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.28.26-33"},"58:28 (26–33)"],"."],["div",{"id":"14b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/5.14b","order":"02.31.005.61343"},["b","14b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/evil"},"TG Evil"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/5.15a","order":"02.31.005.61345"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/love"},"TG Love"],"."],["div",{"id":"15b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/5.15b","order":"02.31.005.61347"},["b","15b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/3.4"},"2 Ne. 3:4"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/25.21"},"25:21"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/2.25"},"Jacob 2:25"],"."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/5.18a","order":"02.31.005.61349"},["b","18a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/5.19.18-19"},"Isa. 5:19 (18–19)"],"."],["div",{"id":"18b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/5.18b","order":"02.31.005.61351"},["b","18b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/joel/1.15"},"Joel 1:15"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/21.20"},"3 Ne. 21:20"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/45.39.39-42"},"D&C 45:39 (39–42)"],"."],["div",{"id":"18c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/5.18c","order":"02.31.005.61353"},["b","18c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/joel/2.2"},"Joel 2:2"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/133.49"},"D&C 133:49"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/js-m/1.33.32-34"},"JS—M 1:33 (32–34)"],"."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/5.21a","order":"02.31.005.61355"},["b","21a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/1.14"},"Isa. 1:14"],"."],["div",{"id":"21b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/5.21b","order":"02.31.005.61357"},["b","21b"],["span.small","IE"],"I will not take heed of your sacrifices, incense, etc."],["div",{"id":"21c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/5.21c","order":"02.31.005.61359"},["b","21c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/solemn-assembly"},"TG Solemn Assembly"],"."],["div",{"id":"22a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/5.22a","order":"02.31.005.61361"},["b","22a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/hypocrisy"},"TG Hypocrisy"],"."],["div",{"id":"22b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/5.22b","order":"02.31.005.61363"},["b","22b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/8.13"},"Hosea 8:13"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/mal/1.10"},"Mal. 1:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"22c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/5.22c","order":"02.31.005.61365"},["b","22c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sacrifice"},"TG Sacrifice"],"."],["div",{"id":"24a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/5.24a","order":"02.31.005.61367"},["b","24a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/amos/6.12"},"Amos 6:12"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/15.7"},"2 Ne. 15:7"],"."],["div",{"id":"24b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/5.24b","order":"02.31.005.61369"},["b","24b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/righteousness"},"TG Righteousness"],"."],["div",{"id":"26a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/5.26a","order":"02.31.005.61371"},["b","26a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/apostasy-of-israel"},"TG Apostasy of Israel"],"."]]}
